Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…亲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到我的公馆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪 快滚出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费尔南·蒙代戈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原将军阁下亲临
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不胜荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这不祥的亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你再也无法口出狂言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你也尝尝被剥夺一切的绝望滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受我复仇的制裁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十三幕\N爱德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是保住了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在吃了药睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂斯坦 这船还能动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在立刻去香榭丽舍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲打算杀了伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰立即离水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标伯爵府
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂斯坦 你那边没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 拜托了 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快服药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 海黛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和岩窟王的契约是绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体已…不再属于我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这世上我唯一想服侍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的言语已无法传达给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想完成最后的复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让您死去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不让您像父亲一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能让你轻易获得安宁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噩梦…消失吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连死也不被容许
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费尔南 看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着肉体和灵魂都已献给这场复仇的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再让您继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不让开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不让开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…因为我爱您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再像那时一样失去所爱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使要我在此失去生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 爱德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主说愿为你献出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 立即扔掉那把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则她就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请服药
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么复仇 什么制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说你从前就是个天真到无可救药的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 你有点得意忘形了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在此为之付出代价吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费尔南 看看你的儿子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令郎的命归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔图乔 开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐 疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若敢扣下那扳机 这家伙也会上西天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙 别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老好人的你逞强也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了我儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔图乔 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道她 她怎样都无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我服从的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 我一个人受伤就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 别再…伤害她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开…放开我儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别夺走我所剩唯一的重要之物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨我吧 恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的命给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以求求你 放他一条命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只求放了我儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我 杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费尔南
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 死是一切的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那不过是从痛苦中解放而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所要的是绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你无尽的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么…倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是…困了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵这样不断的伤害无关的人 图的到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜牺牲母亲甚至海黛小姐 图的到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比人的性命还重要的到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:13:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论自己如何找理由 杀人就是杀人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵、父亲 你们不都只是借此逃避而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样只是固执己见自欺欺人不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:17.80,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你明白朋友的心情？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:17.80,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Tu prétends comprendre ce que ressent ton ami en son fort intérieur？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:23.10,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你明白你可怜的朋友的心情？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:23.10,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}que tu peux comprendre ce qu'éprouves ton pitoyable ami？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约已成立了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.90,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le pacte est conclu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾名为…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon nom nom est
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.90,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Gankutsuou
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔图乔 拿外套来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是您说的「命运」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「命运是要亲手开创的」 不正是您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的意志在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您到哪儿去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间已经到了。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.50,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Il n'est plus temps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救不了他。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.60,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}je ne peux pas le sauver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:25.30,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不明白朋友心情的你救不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:25.30,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}toi qui ignore  ce qu'éprouve un ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我并不明白伯爵真正的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要将你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在亲手杀了他之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也…什么也别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…阿尔贝…在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剑拿来 贝尔图乔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将复仇之剑…交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…必须杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 我答应您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使未来陷入黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使绝望倾泻而来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都一定会活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像您一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能…记住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海黛小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和伯爵在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃的话就请您逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您以为伯爵真希望您死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「希望能记住我的名字」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海黛小姐 您必须活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为比贵族更高贵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人更出色的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那始终不过是建立在谎言的基础之上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以为是的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再逃避了 阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保护好她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑 跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤吧 我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归来吧 我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾名为「岩窟王」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永远与你同在
